snippet.title: 3 Club Golf - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Play VR Golf with a robot in this new release from Duhz Games.  This is a steam VR game, but will soon be available on other platforms.  Thank you for supporting independent developers and solo developers like me...

-Troy
